---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Turf Tech HQ — who we are and why we created this landscaping resource."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">About Turf Tech HQ</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
      Turf Tech HQ is a dedicated resource for homeowners, gardeners, and landscaping professionals who want accurate, practical information about lawn care, garden maintenance, and outdoor living.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
      A beautiful lawn and garden doesn't happen by accident — it takes knowledge, consistency, and the right approach. Our mission is to make high-quality landscaping information accessible to homeowners, DIY gardeners, and lawn care professionals who want to create and maintain stunning outdoor spaces.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">What We Cover</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Lawn care, mowing, and seasonal maintenance</li>
      <li>Garden design, plant selection, and bed installation</li>
      <li>Irrigation systems and watering best practices</li>
      <li>Tree and shrub care, pruning, and trimming</li>
      <li>Soil health, fertilization, and weed control</li>
      <li>Tool reviews and product recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">A Note on Safety</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
      Landscaping work often involves power tools, chemicals, and heavy lifting. Always follow manufacturer guidelines for equipment, wear appropriate protective gear, and consult a professional for work involving large trees, irrigation systems, or grading that exceeds your experience level. The information on Turf Tech HQ is for educational purposes and does not replace professional judgement.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 font-heading">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted">
      Turf Tech HQ participates in the Amazon Associates program. When you purchase products through links on this site, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the content free and up to date.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
